戈夫]]到[[布魯克林籃網|布魯克林籃網]]，獲得第27順位來自[[犹他大学|猶他大學]]的[[凯尔·库兹马|凱爾·庫茲馬]]以及[[布鲁克·洛佩斯|布魯克·羅裴斯]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/nets/news/2017/06/22/brooklyn-nets-acquire-dangelo-russell-and-timofey-mozgov-la-lakers|title=BROOKLYN NETS ACQUIRE D'ANGELO RUSSELL AND TIMOFEY MOZGOV FROM L.A. LAKERS|work=NBA.com|date=2017-06-22|accessdate=2017-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170626004435/http://www.nba.com/nets/news/2017/06/22/brooklyn-nets-acquire-dangelo-russell-and-timofey-mozgov-la-lakers|archive-date=2017-06-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

